a magnifying glass, Nick.

135
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:01,899
I got to get appointed
by the mayor.

136
00:08:01,899 --> 00:08:04,401
You get to meet the mayor?

137
00:08:04,401 --> 00:08:07,613
It's all public.
You could blow this for me.

138
00:08:07,613 --> 00:08:10,365
