because that's not
a very appropriate thing...

809
00:47:07,411 --> 00:47:09,037
for a suicide.

810
00:47:10,664 --> 00:47:13,834
I'm just absolutely not
taking it off.

811
00:47:13,834 --> 00:47:17,921
You are more familiar
with him than I am.

812
00:47:17,921 --> 00:47:19,882
