834
00:48:44,424 --> 00:48:47,845
And maybe we could
have a little talk.

835
00:48:47,845 --> 00:48:50,389
Good. Because I really
need to talk.

836
00:48:50,389 --> 00:48:52,891
You need to talk?
You never need to talk.

837
00:48:52,891 --> 00:48:55,435
